# Project Structure

Keep `src/app/` focused on routing, pages, and UI. Put reusable logic in the appropriate `src/` module.

## `src/app/` — routes and UI only

The App Router folder is for:

- **Pages**: `page.tsx`, `layout.tsx`, `loading.tsx`, `error.tsx`, route segments
- **Route-local components**: colocated UI under `_components/` or feature folders
- **Tests**: `__tests__/` next to the code they cover
- **Framework entry points**: `app/_actions/`, `app/api/`, `app/_components/`

Do **not** add standalone utility modules in `app/`. Pure helpers belong in `src/utils/<domain>/`.

- ✅ Good:

  ```
  src/app/search-typologies/_results/table/results-tabs.tsx
  src/utils/search-typologies/get-search-typologies-filters-resume.ts
  ```

- ❌ Bad:

  ```
  src/app/search-typologies/_results/table/get-search-typologies-filters-resume.ts
  ```

When logic is reused outside one route, move it out of `app/`:

| Kind                              | Location                     |
| --------------------------------- | ---------------------------- |
| Pure helpers, formatters, mappers | `src/utils/<domain>/`        |
| React Query hooks                 | `src/hooks/react-query/`     |
| Other custom hooks                | `src/hooks/`                 |
| Zod schemas and types             | `src/schemas/`, `src/types/` |
| Server-only API calls             | `src/http/`                  |
| Shared UI components              | `src/components/`            |
| React contexts                    | `src/contexts/`              |
| App constants                     | `src/constants/`             |
| Complex local state reducers      | `src/reducers/`              |

## `src/` layout

```
src/
├── app/              # App Router — pages, route UI, tests, _actions, api
├── components/       # Shared UI (ui/, icons/, providers/)
├── contexts/         # React context providers and hooks
├── hooks/            # Custom hooks (react-query/ for query hooks)
├── http/             # Server-only API layer ('server-only')
├── schemas/          # Zod schemas and inferred types
├── utils/            # Pure utilities grouped by domain
├── constants/        # Shared constants
├── config/           # App configuration
├── types/            # Shared TypeScript types
├── reducers/         # useReducer functions for complex local state
├── lib/              # Third-party integrations and shared libs
└── styles/           # Global styles and Tailwind config
```
